rows.label: tlk44500184_01_msg0001
rows.name:
My goodness... Outlanders!
Outlanders are here! I've got to
tell everyone at once!

rows.label: tlk44500184_01_msg0002
rows.name:
From which country did you come?
How fare the other countries?
You must tell me the latest trends...

rows.label: tlk44500184_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh...dreadfully sorry. It's just that
I haven't seen an outlander in so
long... It's such a rare event.

rows.label: tlk44500184_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I thought I was going to kick the bucket
without ever seeing another stranger's
face again...
